Amber Heard has spoken out following JK Rowling’s statement on her decision to keep Johnny Depp in the Fantastic Beasts franchise. Yesterday, Harry Potter author Rowling released a statement on her and director David Yates’ decision to keep Depp in Fantastic Beasts The Crimes of Grindelwald as the character Grindelwald.
